(1. Executive Summary) Tj
T*
(ReLearnAI is a global collaborative learning platform that unifies:) Tj
T*
(- adaptive learning for students) Tj
T*
(- governance and quality control for professors) Tj
T*
(- upskilling and contribution pathways for working professionals) Tj
T*
() Tj
