(2. Problem Statement) Tj
T*
(Learning systems capture abundant interaction data but still fail to deliver trustworthy,) Tj
T*
(actionable next-step guidance.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Three persistent gaps:) Tj
T*
(- learners cannot clearly prioritize what to study next) Tj
T*
(- educators cannot trust ungoverned AI outputs for high-stakes decisions) Tj
T*
(- professional knowledge contributions are disconnected from structured learning pathways) Tj
T*
() Tj
